OL,3,CScrap the Senedd: Inside the fight to
OL,4,Cend devolution
OL,6,FCalum Davies has a dream: He wants to
OL,7,Fgive the Senedd a new purpose: "a
OL,8,Fmuseum to the failed experiment."
OL,10,FSome might find it ironic that the 28-
OL,11,Fyear-old hopes to be elected to the
OL,12,Fchamber at the next Senedd election
OL,13,Fwhile advocating its abolition.
OL,15,F"There's a lot of false promises that
OL,16,Fwe can do things better because
OL,17,Fthere's a Senedd in Cardiff. But
OL,18,Fthat's not really true, is it? Except
OL,19,Ffor recycling, have we done anything
OL,20,Fthat has made Wales better? I don't
OL,21,Fthink so," he says.
