OL,6,FThe Conservative councillor believes
OL,7,Fhis party needs to change its stance
OL,8,Fto become anti-devolution.
OL,10,FAs we sit in a Cardiff coffee shop,
OL,11,Fwith the Senedd looming in the
OL,12,Fbackground, I ask him for his
OL,13,Fimpressions of the Conservative
OL,14,FParty's stance on devolution.
