OL,6,FCalum says not. It isn't about power;
OL,7,Fit's about policy.
OL,9,F"If things aren't getting better, then
OL,10,Fit doesn't have a purpose. You get all
OL,11,Fthese divergent policies`like during
OL,12,Fthe pandemic or the more recent NHS
OL,13,Fapp. You need divergence in order to
OL,14,Fjustify your existence; if you don't
OL,15,Fdiverge, then what are you for?
