OL,6,F"The recent news stories about phonics
OL,7,Fin schools`had we followed what
OL,8,FMichael Gove was doing (the former
OL,9,FEducation Secretary in the UK
OL,10,FGovernment), then imagine how much
OL,11,Fbetter our PISA scores would be."
OL,13,FThe official policy of the
OL,14,FConservative Party is to support Welsh
OL,15,Fdevolution.
OL,17,FIn 2013, the then-Senedd Tory leader,
OL,18,FAndrew RT Davies, told his party they
OL,19,Fmust stick with it:
