OL,6,F"Yes, we must fight for our United
OL,7,FKingdom with all the energy we have,
OL,8,Fbut we must also reflect on where our
OL,9,Fdevolved settlement has arrived.
OL,11,FThere are some who are still fighting
OL,12,Fthe battles of the devolution
OL,13,Freferendum of 1997.
OL,15,FDevolution cannot simply be put back
OL,16,Finto the bottle.
OL,18,FI believe we have reached our 'Clause
OL,19,FIV' moment.
