OL,6,FWe cannot and should not go back to
OL,7,F1997. I fully understand the concerns
OL,8,Fof some who think devolution is about
OL,9,Fmoving towards a breakup of the United
OL,10,FKingdom. These are concerns that I
OL,11,Fshare too, but by ignoring the process
OL,12,Fand not engaging in it, it will not go
OL,13,Faway.
