OL,3,CScrap the Senedd: Inside the fight to
OL,4,Cend devolution
OL,6,FConservatives are about
OL,7,Flocalism`decisions being made as close
OL,8,Fto individuals as possible. This is
OL,9,Fwhat devolution should be about too.
OL,10,FNot a Welsh version of Whitehall, or a
OL,11,Fbureaucracy simply moved down the M4,
OL,12,Fbut Welsh decisions being made in
OL,13,FWales by Wales."
OL,15,FYet, at the Vale of Glamorgan County
OL,16,FShow this summer, Andrew RT Davies
OL,17,Finvited people to have their say on
OL,18,Fabolition, raising eyebrows among his
OL,19,FSenedd colleagues.
