OL,3,CScrap the Senedd: Inside the fight to
OL,4,Cend devolution
OL,6,FThere is one party with one goal: the
OL,7,FAbolish the Welsh Assembly Party.
OL,9,FDespite the Assembly now being called
OL,10,Fthe Senedd, the party is stuck with
OL,11,Fthe name. They also now have a
OL,12,Flogo`something they didn't have even
OL,13,Fat this year's general election.
OL,15,FPaul Ashton, one of the leading
OL,16,Ffigures in the party, says: "We're
OL,17,Ffrom all walks of life, from all
OL,18,Fpolitical parties, with one aim.
OL,19,FDevolution has completely failed the
OL,20,Fpeople of Wales."
