OL,6,FA recent YouGov opinion poll showed
OL,7,F31% of the public support abolition,
OL,8,Fwhile 46% oppose ending devolution.
OL,10,FAbolish believes if they can galvanise
OL,11,Fthat minority vote, they will exceed
OL,12,Fexpectations.
OL,14,F"With the new voting system, we
OL,15,Fbelieve we will have 50
OL,16,Frepresentatives in the Senedd to close
OL,17,Fit down."
