OL,3,CScrap the Senedd: Inside the fight to
OL,4,Cend devolution
OL,6,FAnd if, as polls indicate, they fail?
OL,7,FTheir strategy is to fight the
OL,8,Felection like a referendum: vote
OL,9,FAbolish to abolish or stick with the
OL,10,FSenedd.
OL,12,F"If people don't want to vote for us
OL,13,For the abolishment of devolution, then
OL,14,Fwe will fold as a party," Ashton adds.
OL,16,FFor the Welsh Conservatives, the
OL,17,Fstrategy has been to keep their
OL,18,Fsupporters onside and not vote for
OL,19,FReform or Abolish. But could Abolish
OL,20,Fbe abolished before May 2026? Paul
OL,21,FAshton says it's possible.
