OL,6,F"If a major party came along and
OL,7,Foffered the people of Wales a
OL,8,Freferendum on devolution and fully
OL,9,Fsupported its abolition, then Abolish
OL,10,Fwould fold tomorrow and support that
OL,11,Fparty."
OL,13,FThat's why some Welsh Tories, like
OL,14,FCalum Davies, think the time has come
OL,15,Ffor a change of direction.
OL,17,FBut is this the new Brexit`a decades-
OL,18,Flong internal fight within the Tories?
